<div class="profile-container">
  <div class="profile-header">
    <a href="/">Главная</a> > <span>Мой профиль</span>
  </div>

  <div class="profile-card">
    <div class="profile-content">
      <div class="profile-sidebar">
        <img id="profile-avatar-preview" src="{{avatar}}" alt="Аватар пользователя" class="profile-avatar">
        <label for="profile-avatar-upload" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: 130px%; margin: 10px 0; text-align: center; cursor: pointer;">
          Сменить аватар
        </label>
        <input type="file" id="profile-avatar-upload" accept="image/png, image/jpeg, image/gif" style="display: none;">

        {{{roleSelectHtml}}}
        <div class="profile-info">
          <p><strong>Дата регистрации:</strong> {{registrationDate}}</p>
          <p><strong>Количество реклам:</strong> {{adCount}}</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="profile-main">
        <h2>{{username}}</h2>
        {{#if lastUpdated}}
          <div class="offline-data-indicator">
            <p>Вы в офлайн-режиме. Данные могут быть неактуальны.</p>
            <small>Последнее обновление: {{formatDate lastUpdated}}</small>
          </div>
        {{/if}}

        <form id="profile-form">
          <div class="profile-form-fields">
            {{{loginInputHtml}}}
            {{{emailInputHtml}}}
            {{{firstNameInputHtml}}}
            {{{lastNameInputHtml}}}
            {{{companyInputHtml}}}
            {{{phoneInputHtml}}}
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="profile-form-footer">
      <div class="footer-actions-left">
        {{{deleteButtonHtml}}}
        {{{logoutButtonHtml}}}
      </div>
      {{{saveButtonHtml}}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>